summary:
Professional education on art, art history and theory of education. Experience on a scale of a variety of levels and positions in the fields secondary schools, university, cultural heritage. I like the interaction between these fields, combined with human interest and governance responsibilities. In my professional fields I had the good fortune to put forward my creativity. 
Retired but not tired.
